becomes  more  complex,  and  being  able  to  quickly  target  police,  paramedic  and  fire
services all the more critical.

While today’s hearing will be a bit Colorado-centric, I can tell you that in my con-
gressional  district  along  Florida’s  space  coast,  we  have  experienced  a  dramatic  rise
