What’s  the  most  important  factor  enabling  your  company  to  com-
pete and agree in the global remote sensing industry? And as a fol-
low-on, what role does the government play in promoting a healthy
commercial remote sensing industry.

We  covered  a  little  bit  of  this  ground.  I  want  to  get  this  on  the
record,  and  opportunities  that  will—that  are  present  for  us.  So
we’ll start with Jill.

