85

Ms.  SMITH.  I  think  there  are  two  core  areas  where  the—how
Congress plays out and how the U.S. Government manages the in-
dustry  and  materially  helps  ensure  that  we,  as  an  industry,  are
able  to  retain  leadership.  The  first  is  around  policies  and  regula-
